type.description:
### ⚠️ Requires [Apugli](https://apugli.readthedocs.io/en/latest/) to be installed! ⚠️

## Action On Attacker Hurt

---



[Power Type](https://apugli.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/power_types/action_on_target_hurt)

Executes a bi-entity action upon an entity's current target getting hurt.

Type ID: `apugli:action_on_attacker_hurt`




---

### Examples

```json
{
    "type": "toomanyorigins:action_on_target_hurt",
    "bientity_action": {
        "type": "origins:actor_action",
        "action": {
            "type": "origins:feed",
            "food": 1,
            "saturation": 2.4
        }
    },
    "damage_condition": {
        "type": "origins:or",
        "conditions": [
            {
              "type": "origins:name",
              "name": "wither"
            },
            {
              "type": "origins:name",
              "name": "wither.player"
            }
        ]
    }
}
```
This example feeds the player upon having their current target take damage from damage sources named `wither` or `wither.player`.

